OL,3,CInvestigation launched after man's
OL,4,Cbody found in ditch
OL,6,FAn investigation has been launched
OL,7,Fafter the body of a man was found in a
OL,8,Fditch near Cheltenham.
OL,10,FOfficers discovered the body by the
OL,11,Fside of Old Gloucester Road in
OL,12,FStaverton at around 1.20pm on Sunday 3
OL,13,FMay.
OL,15,FFormal identification has taken place,
OL,16,Fand it is believed to be 62-year-old
OL,17,FAndy Reed, who had been reported
OL,18,Fmissing from the Staverton area on
OL,19,FTuesday 28 April.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
