PN,43902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1778609470
OL,3,CInvestigation launched after man's
OL,4,Cbody found in ditch
OL,6,FHe was last seen at around 10pm on
OL,7,FSaturday 25 April. It is thought that
OL,8,Fhe could have been riding a bright
OL,9,Fblue bike which has yet to be found.
OL,11,FDue to the findings of a post-mortem
OL,12,Fexamination, which revealed a number
OL,13,Fof unexplained injuries, investigating
OL,14,Fofficers are now treating the death as
OL,15,Funexplained and further enquires are
OL,16,Fongoing.
OL,18,FThe man's family has been informed and
OL,19,Fis being supported by specially
OL,20,Ftrained officers.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
