PN,43903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1778609470
OL,3,CInvestigation launched after man's
OL,4,Cbody found in ditch
OL,6,FForensic, CCTV and house-to-house
OL,7,Fenquiries have taken place, and on
OL,8,FSunday 10 May officers from the
OL,9,FSpecialist Operations team, Major
OL,10,FCrime Investigation Team and Criminal
OL,11,FInvestigation Department conducted
OL,12,Ffurther enquires and searches in the
OL,13,FStaverton area.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
