PN,43904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1778609470
OL,3,CInvestigation launched after man's
OL,4,Cbody found in ditch
OL,6,FDetective Inspector Paula Hannaford
OL,7,Ffrom Gloucestershire Constabulary's
OL,8,FCriminal Investigation Department who
OL,9,Fis leading the investigation said:
OL,10,F"Our thoughts remain with Andy's
OL,11,Ffamily at this very difficult time and
OL,12,Fwe are doing all we can to establish
OL,13,Fthe full circumstances around Andy's
OL,14,Fdeath.
OL,16,F"I am appealing to anyone with any
OL,17,Finformation which might help us piece
OL,18,Ftogether what happened to Andy in the
OL,19,Fdays he was missing to please get in
OL,20,Ftouch with the Police.
OL,26,@rD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
