OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1778609470
OL,3,CInvestigation launched after man's
OL,4,Cbody found in ditch
OL,6,F"I would like to hear from anyone who
OL,7,Fmay have seen Andy walking or cycling
OL,8,Falong Old Gloucester Road in Staverton
OL,9,Fbetween 10pm on Saturday 25 April and
OL,10,F1.20pm on Sunday 3 May.
OL,12,F"Andy may have been riding a blue
OL,13,Fwoman's Dutch style bike when he was
OL,14,Flast seen on Saturday 25 April,
OL,15,Fhowever the bike has not yet been
OL,16,Flocated.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1778609470
OL,3,CInvestigation launched after man's
OL,4,Cbody found in ditch
OL,6,F"I am particularly keen for anyone
OL,7,Freading this appeal who was driving
OL,8,Falong Old Gloucester Road between
OL,9,FSaturday 25 April and Sunday 3 May who
OL,10,Fhas access to dashcam footage to
OL,11,Fkindly review their footage for Andy
OL,12,Fand the outstanding bike.
OL,14,F"The bike has a bright blue/turquoise
OL,15,Fframe, a white saddle and metal rack
OL,16,Fabove the rear tyre and is similar to
OL,17,Fthe one pictured below.
OL,26,@vD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1778609470
OL,3,CInvestigation launched after man's
OL,4,Cbody found in ditch
OL,6,F"I would also like to appeal to the
OL,7,Fwider community of Staverton and
OL,8,Fsurrounding area to kindly review
OL,9,Ftheir doorbell and CCTV footage from
OL,10,Fthat time period in case Andy has been
OL,11,Fcaptured.
OL,13,F"Andy was around 6ft tall and of a
OL,14,Fslim build, with stubble facial hair
OL,15,Fand short dark brown hair which was
OL,16,Fthinning on the top.
OL,18,F"He was wearing a blue body warmer
OL,19,Fover a khaki green jumper, brown cords
OL,20,Fand he was carrying a black rucksack."
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/7
